    <title><![CDATA[Borneo's orangutan population plunged by 100,000 since 1999]]></title>
    <link>https://www.ctvnews.ca/sci-tech/borneo-s-orangutan-population-plunged-by-100-000-since-1999-1.3805115</link>
    <description><![CDATA[The most comprehensive study of Borneo's orangutans estimates their numbers have plummeted by more than 100,000 since 1999, as the palm oil and paper industries shrink their jungle habitat and fatal conflicts with people increase.]]></description>
